pr_body:
Meta issue corresponding to [Akmo3/Cytoscape.js](https://github.com/AkMo3/cytoscape.js/) fork https://github.com/AkMo3/cytoscape.js/issues/2

Steps required before merging:
1. Create an environment named `prod` for the secrets to be stored. 
2. Creation of secrets. The secrets are npmjs release secret, github secret for repositories [Cytoscape.js](https://github.com/cytoscape/cytoscape.js) and  [Cytoscape.js-blog](https://github.com/cytoscape/cytoscape.js)
3. Add these secrets to the environment.
